algorithm: The new algorithm calculates the score for each bin by multiplying the reciprocal of the sum of the rest capacities of all bins with a constant value of the logarithm of the item size divided by the sum of the rest capacities of all bins plus the item size.
code:
import numpy as np

def score(item: int, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    sum_rest_capacity = np.sum(bins)
    log_item_size = np.log(item)
    scores = (1 / sum_rest_capacity) * (log_item_size / (sum_rest_capacity + item))
    return scores
